#: ../../theory.rst:5
msgid "理論"
msgstr "Theory"

#: ../../theory.rst:7
msgid ""
"Advance/OF-DFTで使われているAtomic Orbital Facilitated DFT(AOF-"
"DFT)について、要素となる理論を解説します。"
msgstr ""
"This page explains the underlying theory of Atomic Orbital Facilitated "
"DFT (AOF-DFT) used in Advance/OF-DFT."

#: ../../theory.rst:12
msgid "Orbital-Free DFT(OF-DFT)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../theory.rst:14
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"密度汎関数理論(Density Functional Theory, DFT)は、系の電子密度 "
":math:`\\rho(\\mathbf{r})` の汎関数としてエネルギー :math:`E[\\rho]` が与えられ"
"、エネルギーを最小化することで基底状態の電子密度が得られるというHohenberg-Kohnの定理に基づきます。"
msgstr ""
"Density Functional Theory (DFT) is based on the Hohenberg-Kohn theorem, "
"which states that the energy :math:`E[\\rho]` is given as a functional of"
" the system's charge density :math:`\\rho(\\mathbf{r})` , and the ground "
"state charge density can be obtained by minimizing the energy."

#: ../../theory.rst:16
msgid ""
"DFTに基づく第一原理電子状態計算の標準的な手法となっているKohn-Sham DFT(KS-DFT)では"
"、仮想的な参照系として相互作用のないKohn-Sham系を導入し、エネルギー汎関数の運動エネルギー項の計算にKS系の波動関数（Kohn-"
"Sham軌道） :math:`\\psi_i` を使います。"
msgstr ""
"In Kohn-Sham DFT (KS-DFT), which is the standard method for first-"
"principles electronic structure calculations based on DFT, a non-"
"interacting Kohn-Sham system is introduced as a hypothetical reference "
"system, and the wave functions of the KS system (Kohn-Sham orbitals) "
":math:`\\psi_i` are used to calculate the kinetic energy term of the "
"energy functional."

#: ../../theory.rst:18
msgid ""
"& E[\\rho] = \\underset{\\mathrm{Kinetic}}{T[\\rho]} + "
"\\underset{\\mathrm{External Potential}}{E_\\mathrm{ext}[\\rho]} + "
"\\underset{\\mathrm{Hartree(Coulomb)}}{E_H[\\rho]} + "
"\\underset{\\mathrm{Exchange Correlation}}{E_\\mathrm{XC}[\\rho]}\n"
"\n"
"& T_\\mathrm{KS}[\\rho] = "
"-\\frac{1}{2}\\sum_{i}\\langle\\psi_i\\lvert\\nabla^2\\rvert\\psi_i\\rangle"
msgstr ""

#: ../../theory.rst:24
msgid ""
"KS軌道はKS方程式の固有関数であり、KS-DFTでは固有値問題を数値的に解く必要があります。これが原子数 :math:`N` に対し計算量が "
":math:`O(N^3)` となり、「第一原理計算が重い」と言われる理由です。"
msgstr ""
"KS orbitals are eigenfunctions of the KS equation, and KS-DFT requires "
"solving the eigenvalue problem numerically. This leads to a computational"
" complexity of :math:`O(N^3)` with respect to the number of atoms "
":math:`N` , which is why first-principles calculations are said to be "
"\"heavy\"."

#: ../../theory.rst:26
msgid ""
"これに対し、運動エネルギー汎関数の計算にKS軌道を使わず(Orbital-Free)、計算量を :math:`O(N)` に抑えよう"
"、というのがOF-DFTの考え方です。元々のDFT(Hohenberg-Kohn DFT)に近いですが、運動エネルギー汎関数 "
":math:`T[\\rho]` はKS-DFTと同様に相互作用のない参照系で定義します。"
msgstr ""
"In contrast, the concept of OF-DFT is to limit the computational "
"complexity to :math:`O(N)` without using KS orbitals (Orbital-Free) for "
"calculating the kinetic energy functional. Although it is similar to the "
"original DFT (Hohenberg-Kohn DFT), the kinetic energy functional "
":math:`T[\\rho]` is defined in a non-interacting reference system, just "
"as in KS-DFT."

#: ../../theory.rst:28
msgid "KS-DFTとOF-DFT、および分子動力学で使われる力場法を比較します。"
msgstr ""
"We compare KS-DFT, OF-DFT, and force field methods used in molecular "
"dynamics."

