msgstr "Field :math:`\\mathbf{h}(\\mathbf{r})`"

#: ../../theory.rst:91
#, python-brace-format
msgid "隣接行列 :math:`a_{ij}`"
msgstr "Adjacency matrix :math:`a_{ij}`"

#: ../../theory.rst:91
#, python-brace-format
msgid "隣接相関 :math:`a(\\mathbf{r}, \\mathbf{r}')`"
msgstr "Adjacency correlation :math:`a(\\mathbf{r}, \\mathbf{r}')`"

#: ../../theory.rst:93
msgid "特徴量の集約"
msgstr "Aggregation of features"

#: ../../theory.rst:93
msgid "隣接相関を積分核とする畳み込み積分"
msgstr "Convolution integral using adjacency correlation as the integral kernel"

#: ../../theory.rst:96
msgid ""
"隣接相関 :math:`a(\\mathbf{r}, \\mathbf{r}')` は定義上は :math:`\\mathbf{R} = "
"\\mathbf{r} - \\mathbf{r}'` "
"で非ゼロの値を持つデルタ関数になりますが、数値計算を行うために、動径方向に幅を持つガウス関数で置き換えます。角度方向には球対称とし、球平均を取って距離のみの関数にします。"
msgstr ""
"By definition, the adjacency correlation :math:`a(\\mathbf{r}, \\mathbf{r}')` "
"is a delta function taking non-zero values at :math:`\\mathbf{R} = "
"\\mathbf{r} - \\mathbf{r}'` ; however, for numerical calculations, we "
"replace it with a Gaussian function having a width in the radial direction. "
"We assume spherical symmetry in the angular direction and take a spherical "
"average to make it a function of distance only."

#: ../../theory.rst:98
msgid ""
"a(\\mathbf{r}, \\mathbf{r}') = a\\left(|\\mathbf{r} - "
"\\mathbf{r}'|\\right) = \\int \\mathrm{d}\\Omega "
"\\frac{1}{\\left(\\sqrt{2\\pi}\\kappa\\right)^3} "
"\\exp\\left(-\\frac{|\\mathbf{r}-\\mathbf{r}'-\\mathbf{R}|^2}{2\\kappa^2}\\right)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../theory.rst:102
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"半径 :math:`R` 、幅 :math:`\\kappa` がパラメータとなります。種々の :math:`\\{R_i, "
"\\kappa_i\\}` 対に対する :math:`a_i\\left(|\\mathbf{r} - "
"\\mathbf{r}'|\\right)` "
"を使って特徴量を集約することで、空間全体をカバーするようなマルチチャンネル化を行ったことになります。畳み込み積分の距離を有限にするため、カットオフ関数"
" :math:`f_i` を適用します。"
msgstr ""
"The radius :math:`R` and width :math:`\\kappa` serve as parameters. By "
"aggregating features using :math:`a_i\\left(|\\mathbf{r} - "
"\\mathbf{r}'|\\right)` for various pairs of :math:`\\{R_i, \\kappa_i\\}` , we "
"effectively implement multi-channeling that covers the entire space. To "
"limit the range of the convolution integral, we apply a cutoff function "
":math:`f_i` ."

#: ../../theory.rst:104
msgid "最終的に、汎グラフのGCNは次のように定式化されます。"
msgstr "Finally, the Graphical GCN is formulated as follows."

#: ../../theory.rst:106
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"& x_{\\mu i}^n(\\mathbf{r}) = f_i \\int \\mathrm{d}\\mathbf{r}' "
"a_i(|\\mathbf{r} - \\mathbf{r}'|)h_\\mu^n(\\mathbf{r}')\n"
"\n"
"& h_\\nu^{n+1}(\\mathbf{r}) = h_\\nu^n(\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\sigma\\left(\\sum_{\\mu i}w_{\\nu,\\mu i}^n x_{\\mu "
"i}^n(\\mathbf{r})\\right)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../theory.rst:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":math:`\\mathbf{r}` が連続のままであることに注目してください。数値計算を行う上では離散的な "
":math:`\\mathbf{r}` "
"（メッシュ）を使いますが、汎グラフのGCNのパラメータはメッシュの細かさに依存しません。学習時と推論時でメッシュの細かさや形が異なっていても良く、transferabilityが高いのが特長です。"
msgstr ""
"Note that :math:`\\mathbf{r}` remains continuous. Although a discrete "
":math:`\\mathbf{r}` (mesh) is used for numerical calculations, the "
"parameters of the Graphical GCN are independent of the mesh resolution. The "
"mesh resolution and shape can differ between training and inference, "
"offering the advantage of high transferability."

#: ../../theory.rst:116
msgid "汎グラフを使った運動エネルギー汎関数AdvanceSoft25は図のようなアーキテクチャになります。汎グラフに入力する特徴ベクトルとしては、電子密度の勾配、ラプラシアン（＋オプションとして勾配とラプラシアンの積）を使います。"
msgstr ""
"The architecture of the kinetic energy functional AdvanceSoft25 using "
"Graphical is as shown in the figure. The feature vectors input to Graphical "
"are the gradient of the charge density and the Laplacian (plus, "
"optionally, the product of the gradient and the Laplacian)."

#: ../../theory.rst:118
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"出力はThomas-Fermi(TF)モデルおよびvon Weizsäcker(vW)モデルで計算した運動エネルギー密度 "
":math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r})` に対する補強因子 "
":math:`F^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})` として使い、最終的な運動エネルギーを得ます。"
msgstr ""
"The output is used as an enhancement factor "
":math:`F^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})` for the kinetic energy density "
":math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r})` calculated using the Thomas-Fermi (TF) and von "
"Weizsäcker (vW) models, to obtain the final kinetic energy."

#: ../../theory.rst:120
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"T_\\mathrm{AS25}[\\rho] = \\int \\mathrm{d}\\mathbf{r} "
"\\lbrace\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r})F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})"
" + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r})F_\\mathrm{vW}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})\\rbrace"
msgstr ""

#: ../../theory.rst:127
msgid "局所密度行列汎関数理論(L-DMFT)"
msgstr "Local Density Matrix Functional Theory (L-DMFT)"

#: ../../theory.rst:129
msgid ""
"AdvanceSoft25を使ったSCF計算では、既存の機械学習汎関数に比べて電子密度の再現性が高いことが確認できたものの"
"、原子核付近の記述の精度に問題があるというOF-"
"DFT自体の問題は依然として存在し、特にイオン結晶のような電子が局在した系で誤差が大きくなってしまう問題があります。"
msgstr ""
"In SCF calculations using AdvanceSoft25, while it has been confirmed that the "
"reproducibility of the charge density is higher compared to existing "
"machine learning functionals, the inherent problem of OF-DFT regarding the "
"accuracy of the description near atomic nuclei still remains. In particular, "
"there is an issue where errors become significant in systems with localized "
"electrons, such as ionic crystals."

#: ../../theory.rst:131
msgid ""
"これに対し、原子ごとの局所的な密度行列は厳密に扱い、原子間は電子密度の汎関数で補完する局在密度行列汎関数理論(Localized Density "
"Matrix Functional Theory, L-DMFT)を導入しました。"
msgstr ""
"To address this, we introduced Localized Density Matrix Functional Theory "
"(L-DMFT), which rigorously treats the local density matrix of each atom "
"while complementing the inter-atomic region with an charge density "
"functional."

#: ../../theory.rst:133
msgid ""
"局所的な波動関数としてはOpenMXの擬原子軌道(Pseudo Atomic Orbital, "
"PAO)をそのまま使い、局所密度行列を最適化します。これにより、純粋なOF-"
"DFTでは難しかったDFT+U（電子相関の補正）やスピン軌道相互作用といった、局所的な物理現象を扱えるようになります。"
msgstr ""
"We use Pseudo Atomic Orbitals (PAO) from OpenMX as-is for the local wave "
"functions and optimize the local density matrix. This enables the handling "
"of local physical phenomena such as DFT+U (correction for electron "
"correlation) and spin-orbit coupling, which were difficult to achieve with "
"pure OF-DFT."

